<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>السنين.<span class="c5"> وفُسِّر به قوله تعالى:</span> <span class="c3">{إِلَى أُمَّةٍ مَعْدُودَةٍ}</span> <span class="c2">((٨)</span>)<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
